strings: <voice_0x010008CE><se_low>Yangus: Oi! Guv!
<voice_0x010008CF><se_low>Yangus: It's gonna get dark if we 'ang about 'ere much longer.

<voice_0x010008D0><se_low>Yangus: Let's 'ead inta town.
There's better places than this to spend an evenin'!
<voice_0x010008D1><se_low>Yangus: Shake a leg, guv!
<voice_0x01001DBD><se_low>Trode: (Mumble grumble...)
<voice_0x010008D3><se_low>Yangus: I've prob'ly said it before, but it beats me 'ow you ended up workin' for an old codger like 'im!
<voice_0x010008D4><se_low>Yangus: Not that I can talk, though, eh!? Guess people say the same thing about me workin' for you.

<voice_0x010008D5><se_low>Trode: Hm? Old codger!?
I do hope you're not referring to me!

<voice_0x010008D6><se_low>Trode: What would you know!?
A lowlife like you wouldn't recognise nobility
if it came up and bit you on the...arrrgh!

<voice_0x010008D7><se_low>Trode: Enough dilly-dallying! <Cap><hero>!
Where's the Princess? I can't see her anywhere...
<voice_0x010008D8><se_low>Yangus: Uh-oh! Here comes trouble, guv!

<voice_0x010008D9><se_low>Trode: Well...they certainly took us by surprise.
But nothing we couldn't handle, eh!?

<voice_0x010008DA><se_low>Trode: Now, where's the Princess!?
Where's my Medea!?
My precious one and only daughter!?

<voice_0x010008DB><se_low>Trode: Ah! There you are!
Thank goodness you're safe, Medea!
<voice_0x010008DC><se_low>Yangus: Aye-aye, the 'orse-princess is back...
<voice_0x010008DD><se_low>Yangus: I say we make a move now, before it gets dark.
<voice_0x010008DE><se_low>Trode: Yes. Yes! Here we are. If my memory serves me correctly, this is the place.
<voice_0x010008DF><se_low>Trode: This is the town where Master Rylus lives.

<voice_0x010008E0><se_low>Yangus: Hold yer 'orses, Grandad!
I thought it was Dhoulmagus we was after.
<voice_0x010008E1><se_low>Trode: I AM NOT YOUR GRANDAD! And of course Dhoulmagus is our man! He's the one who turned Medea and I into such laughing stocks!
<voice_0x010008E2><se_low>Trode: But that dastardly magician can't hide from us forever!
<voice_0x010008E3><se_low>Trode: We must track him down and lift this confounded curse!
<voice_0x010008E4><se_low>Trode: Oh! Just look at my poor Medea!

<voice_0x010008E5><se_low>Trode: And we'd only just settled on her engagement
to the Prince of Argonia... Oh, that despicable Dhoulmagus!

<voice_0x010008E6><se_low>Trode: That's why it's imperative we locate Rylus!
Will you go and find him, <hero>?
<voice_0x010008E7><se_low>Trode: That's the spirit! I knew I could rely on you, <hero>! I'll be waiting here.
<voice_0x010008E8><se_low>Trode: Bu<endash> D-Don't you see!? Rylus is the very man who taught Dhoulmagus his meddlesome magic!
<voice_0x010008E9><se_low>Trode: There's every chance he'll be able to give us a clue as to the whereabouts of that evil rogue.
<voice_0x010008E9><se_low>Trode: There's every chance he'll be able to give us a clue as to the whereabouts of that evil rogue.

<voice_0x010008EA><se_low>Trode: That's why you must find him.
I'll be waiting for you here.
<se_low>Yangus: Guv! Over 'ere!
